411
00:23:21,650 --> 00:23:26,650
"Kantor Detektif Mouri."

412
00:23:29,950 --> 00:23:32,850
Inspektur, ini Mouri.

413
00:23:32,850 --> 00:23:37,250
Aku akan menghapus tanda kantor detektif aku mulai hari ini.

414
00:23:37,250 --> 00:23:38,550
Ayah.

415
00:23:39,650 --> 00:23:40,850
Ayah.

416
00:23:43,750 --> 00:23:44,750
Tuan Mouri?

417
00:23:44,750 --> 00:23:46,450
