419
00:23:49,450 --> 00:23:51,250
Tolong, ayah.

420
00:23:51,250 --> 00:23:53,450
Pikirikan lagi.

421
00:23:53,450 --> 00:23:54,850
Ayah!

422
00:23:57,250 --> 00:24:00,450
Lagi pula, kau mempertahankannya selama sepuluh tahun.

423
00:24:00,450 --> 00:24:02,150
Aku yakin kau pasti kelelahan.

424
00:24:02,150 --> 00:24:03,850
Ibu.

